com.exacttarget.fuelsdk

Class ETTriggeredEmail

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.exacttarget.fuelsdk.ETObject
      • com.exacttarget.fuelsdk.ETApiObject
        • com.exacttarget.fuelsdk.ETSoapObject
          • com.exacttarget.fuelsdk.ETTriggeredEmail

  • public class ETTriggeredEmail
extends ETSoapObject
    An ETTriggeredEmail represents a Triggered Email in the Salesforce Marketing Cloud. Triggered Emails are created in the Marketing Cloud Email app under the Interactions menu: Terminology note: Triggered Emails are sometimes referred to as "Triggered Sends" in the Email app, and the SOAP API refers to Triggered Emails as "Triggered Send Definitions".
